userPromptForThisRevision: pull internet trends from reddit, github, google trends, wikipedia, and build a dashboard around that information.

imageAssets.description: Abstract, dark-themed background image for a data trends dashboard. Subtle, flowing lines of light (like fiber optics or data streams) in shades of deep blue, teal, and hints of purple, on a very dark gray or near-black background (#0A0E12). Evokes technology, data flow, and sophistication. Not too busy, should allow text and cards to be easily readable on top. Maybe a faint grid or constellation-like pattern in the deep background.
imageAssets.purpose: Main background for the entire dashboard (body tag). Filename suggestion: 'dashboard_background.png'

imageAssets.description: Monochromatic icon for Reddit. Stylized Reddit Snoo alien head, simple and clean. Color: light gray (#ADB5BD) or white, suitable for dark theme. Flat design, no gradients.
imageAssets.purpose: Icon for Reddit trends card header. Filename suggestion: 'icon_reddit.png'
